quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  10,15,aur jab un ko hamari ayatain parh kar sunai jati hain to jin logon ko hum se milnay ki umeed nahi woh kehte hain ke ( ya to ) is ke siwa koi aur quran ( bana ) lao ya is ko badal do. keh do ke mujh ko ikhtiyar nahi hai ke usay apni taraf se badal do. mein to isi hukum ka tabay hon jo meri taraf aata hai. agar mein apne perwar-digaar ki nafarmani karoon to mujhe barray ( sakht ) din ke azaab se khauf aata hai
  10,16,( yeh bhi ) keh do ke agar khuda chahta to ( nah to ) mein hi yeh ( kitaab ) tum ko parh kar sunataa aur nah wohi tumhe is se waaqif karta. mein is se pehlay tum mein aik Umar raha hon ( aur kabhi aik kalma bhi is terhan ka nahi kaha ) bhala tum samajte nahi
  10,17,to is se barh kar zalim kon jo khuda par jhoot aftara kere aur is ki ayaton ko jhutlaye. be shak gunehgaar Falah nahi payen ge
  10,18,aur yeh ( log ) khuda ke siwa aisi cheezon ki parastish karte hain jo nah un ka kuch bigaar hi sakti hain aur nah kuch bhala hi kar sakti hain aur kehte hain ke yeh khuda ke paas hamari sifarish karne walay hain. keh do kekiya tum khuda ko aisi cheez batatay ho jis ka wujood usay nah asmano mein maloom hota hai aur nah zameen mein. woh pak hai aur ( is ki shaan ) un ke shirk karne se bohat buland hai
  10,19,aur ( sab ) log ( pehlay ) aik hi aُmt ( yani aik hi millat par ) they. phir judda judda hogaye. aur agar aik baat jo tumahray perwar-digaar ki taraf se pehlay hochuki hai nah hoti to jin baton mein woh ikhtilaaf karte hain un mein faisla kar diya jata
  10,20,aur kehte hain ke is par is ke perwar-digaar ki taraf se koi nishani kyun nazil nahi hui. keh do ke ghaib ( ka ilm ) to khuda ko hai so tum intzaar karo. mein bhi tumahray sath intzaar karta hon
